# Baseline .gitignore for C++ assignments that do NOT provide one.
# (If an assignment provides its own, study it — never replace or edit it.)
#
# This file ignores legitimate build/editor/OS artifacts only. ENGINE AND
# TOOLING (.claude/, .clang-format, the AI log, the PDF) are ignored locally via
# .git/info/exclude so the committed .gitignore stays a clean project artifact
# and a provided one is never modified.

# Build artifacts
*.o
*.obj
*.gch
*.pch
*.so
*.a
a.out
*.out
*.exe
build/
bin/

# Editor / IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*~

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
